data.text: @e_lisney @soktahu YUM. That will be 2019, lemme finish my upgrade in March tho!
@mailbykite @soktahu Rendang remark was aimed at Annabel! Didn't invite you because I know you should be focused on your phd. When you finish I promise you a big makan!  Very big makan!
@e_lisney @soktahu Annabel and I are Minang/Padang, so specific to that. :)
@mailbykite @soktahu It's mostly mak cik in Malaysia. Not heard of the other ones. I don't like being called auntie either I know it's a sign of respect...

@soktahu @e_lisney Wow, never heard of that setup before. Usually Mak Tuo = oldest aunt in that family. Everyone else who's a woman is Etek/Tek (which is what I insist nephews and nieces call me, even if everyone else is Auntie/Tante!).
@mailbykite @soktahu Nope I didn't notice anything...but don't you dare call me mak cik! I won't respond
@e_lisney @soktahu don't think i can make saturday xxx we should all rendang soon though... - etek

@e_lisney @soktahu I call everyone mak cik though, Eleanor, even me... :) And yes, of course I am older than Dek Annabel, bc you might notice way too many '90s references around me... This is why I tend to wear glasses at conferences.
@soktahu @mailbykite Hey if you want you can bring sending on Saturday this has made me rendang craving...

@soktahu @mailbykite Really didn't realise that you're older Okka but i m so old I ll be a mak cik
!
@soktahu Ha!! Who have you been talking to, you've only met one of my exes x Much love, Adek
@soktahu might we say... :: lowers glasses :: rendang-cookinglike?
@soktahu Back at you! So weird to be a beacon of energy w chronic fatigue ^^ ❤️❤️❤️
